00:13:02.170 --> 00:13:02.830
All right.

00:13:02.830 --> 00:13:07.210
So now let's say you
want to calculate

00:13:07.210 --> 00:13:16.780
the the uncertainty
of x in phi n.

00:13:16.780 --> 00:13:21.280
Well, the uncertainty
of x squared

00:13:21.280 --> 00:13:23.980
