00:17:18.280 --> 00:17:21.099
OK, that-- now we--

00:17:21.099 --> 00:17:24.740
maybe it's a little
more interesting.

00:17:24.740 --> 00:17:27.200
But again, you should
you should refuse

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:29.030
