it's 1 plus n hat.

00:19:10.267 --> 00:19:17.470
And Therefore x squared
expectation value has become

00:19:17.470 --> 00:19:24.970
h bar over 2mw phi m, and
this whole parenthesis

00:19:24.970 --> 00:19:31.280
